'''黑岩俊喜'''（{{lang-ja| くろいわ としき}}，{{bd|1993年|8月31日|||Toshiki Kuroiwa}}）是一位[[日本|日本]][[雪車|雪車]]運動員。<ref name="fibtprofile">{{Cite web |url=http://www.fibt.com/bobsleigh/athletes.html?athl_id=129964 |title=FIBT Profile |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-date=2014-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140226005338/http://www.fibt.com/bobsleigh/athletes.html?athl_id=129964 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

俊喜代表日本參加[[2014年冬季奧運|2014年冬季奧運]]。他為駕駛和[[宮崎久|宮崎久]]、[[佐藤真太郎|佐藤真太郎]]、[[鈴木寬|鈴木寬]]等人在男子四人項目中得到26名。<ref name="sportsrefprofile">{{cite web|title=Sports Reference Profile|url=http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ku/toshiki-kuroiwa-1.html|accessdate=2016-02-06|archive-date=2014-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140505040203/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ku/toshiki-kuroiwa-1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="sochi2014profile">{{cite web|title=Sochi2014.com profile|date=March 19, 2014|url=http://www.sochi2014.com/en/athlete-toshiki-kuroiwa|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140319224800/http://www.sochi2014.com/en/athlete-toshiki-kuroiwa|archivedate=2014-03-19|accessdate=2016-02-06}}</ref>

